  <brief_title>Safety of Same Day Discharge After Elective Percutaneous Coronary Intervention</brief_title>
  <official_title>Feasibility and Safety of Same Day Discharge After Elective Percutaneous Coronary Intervention (PCI) in a Tertiary Care Hospital in Karachi, Pakistan.</official_title>
